To use my custom url field:

Example:

from django.db import models
from customurlfield.fields import URLField


class TestModel(models.Model):
    customurl = URLField(default_protocol="http",protocols=["https","ssh","spdy"])
                                                 # protocols must be a list.




This url field checks that the protocol is accepted (being in default_protocol, or protocols.) 
if there is no protocol, it prepends the default protocol to the url.
